init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So, he works on making himself a more acceptable boyfriend to her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He eventually realizes that he doesn't need to be a different person, but needs to become a better version of himself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's a great dancer, but he can't dance very well in front of her so he starts taking lessons.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells her everything he's learned and how he's improved himself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is stunned and cries in her arms.
